The most magical moment of my entire life ~ saying yes to my forever!!! 🌹💍

Starting the day with breakfast at @grandhotelmenaggio (a must stay when visiting Lake Como!!! From the boutique style rooms, most delicious breakfast buffet, AND an infinity pool over looking the lake - you’re living a dream.) Shortly after we took the ferry over to Bellagio - BEAUTIFUL but veryyy touristy 🙃 we grabbed lunch, wine tasted and headed back to our hotel in Menaggio to get ready for the photoshoot at @villamonastero_official in Veranna - the most colorful village on the lake. I booked with @stefaniemouraphoto (you’re amazing and we love you SOOO much!!! Words will never describe the gratitude for you, capturing our connection & this moment we’ll get to hold onto forever 🥲❤️ I cannot recommend her enough!!). 

Being a couples photographer, and especially in Lake Como - it was a must for me to get photos of us while we were there. Little did I know, Cristian searched Stefanie on Instagram and messaged her about the surprise proposal. These two coordinated the best moment of my life to have it captured. I could write a whole novel about how much that means to me from a photographers stand point but we’ll save that for another time 🤭🤍 I thought I could pick up on most things - especially the day I would get engaged, but I WAS SO WRONG. 😅 Cristian was probably the most chill I’ve ever seen him lol meanwhile I 10000% hyperventilated when it happened with 0 shame. Right as I turned around, it started raining! I have chills writing this because it truly was the most beautiful experience! We’re still soaring on cloud 9 and cannot WAITTT to plan the best day of our lives!! ✨
Thank you again for all the love and support we’ve received ❤️😭 we are so grateful!!!! 

#italyproposal #lakecomo #wereengaged #isaidyes #engagementphotos #varenna #menaggio

Happy first birthday, Saint! 🤍

How do you expect a hurricane to hit SoCal in August a year and half out from your wedding date? You simply can’t. But you can choose to make the most of it with all your loved ones and continue living the day in hopes it exceeds all expectations from what you first imagined it would be like. I heavily admire Monica and Joe for this reason. When I received the text “rain or shine, it’s happening regardless” from Monica, it put the biggest smile on my face. Nothing, not even nature, should dictate how you envisioned this day to be for the two of you. And knowing that is the best part. Making it your own and thriving in the element of how the day chooses to unfold in its own particular way. 💫 Biggest congratulations to you both! It was an honor to document this special day and letting it happen exactly as it was suppose to. 🌧️✨☔️
